;;
;; COVERAGE NOTE (G5): "authoritative" here = maintainer-verified against primary
;; sources, the real-data tier above :representative. Writing these datoms INTO the
;; live kotoba gov-atlas-v1 graph still needs an operator token + node (KOTOBA_TOKEN),
;; and PUBLISHING national :authoritative rows to /.well-known/gov-units.json is the
;; Council-Lv6+ / bootstrap-attestation gate (validate_atlas.py check #5). This file
;; is the committed registry record; ingest + publish are separate operator steps.
;;
;; QID INTEGRITY: a prior demo wave fabricated a contiguous fake block (Q1023xxx)
;; (e.g. MOF "Q1023766" = CIUTI, a Brussels translators' association). All re-verified.
;;
;; G20 = 19 sovereign states + the EU. The EU has no single finance ministry (fiscal
;; policy = European Commission DG ECFIN + the Eurogroup), so no finance child is
;; asserted for it (honest, not an omission).

